Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.15,0:01:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会成为敌人的人多半都很顽固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由驾驶员升起来的指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不乖乖坐着指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.88,0:01:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还开出反管制品的MS出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.92,0:01:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之他被我打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是Z高达的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我太有实力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 咖扎的风暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.14,0:02:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们所在的地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛应该是躲在这边的废铁堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确切位置尚未掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.21,0:02:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以亚加玛想出外的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定得先经过我们才能抵达港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必再解释了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计算亚加玛的最短距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用安多拉的主炮轰它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地内用战舰主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让市民知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量就代表正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我不听新的提案\N潘帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到这样就无法替朋友报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便心痛不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们驾驶员究竟是为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要日夜训练驾驶MS呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我打败Z高达的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是真正的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人一定很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就暂时交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,谢谢大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛到底躲在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要去收破烂的集会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,工业用舱口\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们在管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们解释一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会打开舱口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快让亚加玛离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然会被敌人打坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些收破烂的会乐死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又多了好多铁屑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前殖民地就先完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是讲不听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人都跟盖蒙差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你说我什么阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,那个...快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉的居民都在注意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.72,0:05:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定要光明正大的打赢战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会做出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有辱大人名誉的卑鄙行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,去吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克暴风部队,出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕,比安,做出那个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人,我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比安,潘帕,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太善解人意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.44,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克部队,尽量的表现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下路阿,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直待在破烂堆中有点无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的名声都快臭掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在埋在垃圾堆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都快生锈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是布拉杜舰长不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一点进步也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮忙,奇马达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长,抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑\N好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,等一下\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了慎重起见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边的垃圾山也要调查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘帕,,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比安,你跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人呢...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两架新型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花,去开动Z高达去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯,你去开动密达斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?确定吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你去开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭老头...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有MS你只是普通的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳头对我是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛\N那时候我有救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要扭断你的骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别档着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达跟密达斯\N去引开敌人的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之间快疏散平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联络到捷度吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了,Z高达出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长,请让我动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,潘帕,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要光明正大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一对一决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人的MS!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,潘帕,比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市民在看阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就想逃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手阿,比安!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背后攻击是卑鄙小人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的..?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我好像得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从背后攻击太卑鄙了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这样就没意见了吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!会断掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要替肯丁报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他像我弟弟一样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟我无关!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个驾驶员!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉的各位市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.77,0:10:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正与亚加玛的MS作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有绝对数量的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却要求做一对一的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我们不想伤害殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相较之下,亚加玛卑鄙透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们偷偷摸摸的逃进殖民地内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.96,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全没考虑殖民地的损害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的战舰不也进入殖民地里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛准备出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那种没脸皮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛紧急出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引开敌人注意力\N支援Z高达跟密达斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加马准备出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各岗位人员各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道用法吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以随便让我玩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有能源调节装置吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说有调节装置\N在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被迫采取非常手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,责任完全在亚加玛身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛给所有人带来麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就麻烦的更彻底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请各位市民协助...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没打中阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在调节哪里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想破坏殖民地吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉的各位市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到刚才亚加玛的攻击了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是卑鄙的偷袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算会毁掉整各殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要战斗到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要恨就恨亚加玛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开捷度阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的厉害吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重,好重阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是本地人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道亚加玛躲在哪里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何只知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就带我去亚加玛吧\N当作回报我的救命之恩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是带路的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉比安罗兹的露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹的露卡...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是桥,别掉下去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子到哪里去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才发光的地方可能有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?刚才的小飞机是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在这一带...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌\N那是Z高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我第一眼看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达会这么惨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是援军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的追兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的战斗机是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用正当攻法了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧,Z高达!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚...糟了\N踩不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员还没死?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来引开敌人,你快逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的战机是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必管那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是Z高达,到底躲到哪里了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长,其实我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那战斗机是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,你干麻像木头\N一样站着不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完了,Z高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么车子...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来换班,你得请我吃一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那也是敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.13,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在跟敌人的MS交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,听见了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一架由我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一架给你应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉比安罗兹的露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的...你没有问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这边是Z高达\N小心别受到波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为在殖民地内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以胡作非为吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地层下陷了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定那是核战机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,是从拉比安罗兹飞来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫个炮座支援核战机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核战机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请到亚加码的射程内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源调整完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太弱就没意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了,真痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疑!逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的Z高达!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不出来,我就逼你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地被开了个洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有弥补的机关...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按错了...这是机关炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次在受到攻击\N殖民地一定会被打个大洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会在容忍你们放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗?比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,潘帕,使用烟雾模式\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了大气层内的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而专门研发出的战法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在烟雾中\N你就施展不出手脚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要如何分辨敌人的位置?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的米诺夫斯基粒子\N已经破坏了雷达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.99,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照计算\N烟雾应该只会盖住我们的机身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾扩散的比预计的快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双方条件都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方数目还比较多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一颗会中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乱七八糟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去,殖民地会毁灭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么烟雾..?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达,你没事吧...!\NZ高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题可大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去,殖民地会毁灭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用无线电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被发现位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个烟雾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不消除烟雾就很难瞄准...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾是因为空气而扩散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别太过分!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉!\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾...怎么不见了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!你竟敢伤害比安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险!\N注意后方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.66,0:20:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨克部队竟然全灭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取消出航命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.09,0:20:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对Z高达还研究不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急措施做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给殖民地公署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回亚加码吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹是修理船的船屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉度舰长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹在等亚加码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来的好,我等了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能想办法打开工业用舱口?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能久留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.92,0:21:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人马上就会攻过来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,我试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然照这样下去\N殖民地真的会被破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家走吧,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.99,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是开核战机进来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么说你有好方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.85,0:22:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有阿\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核战机跟亚加码的大小差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.45,0:22:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我痛打一顿的大叔还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.78,0:22:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是杀也杀不死的

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘恩负义人到处都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逸扎原本可是我们救上来的人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.75,0:23:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次他却用两台盖杰攻过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边Z却不听使唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 给我好好地行动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是NEWTYPE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么武断啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二度敲响镇魂的钟声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了
